Everything

PS Cafe is a delicious refuge from the shopping noise of Orchard. Beautiful, light filled interior is a great setting for lively lunches. Bites are inventive and desserts are a must try.
love the truffle friess! Ask for lala, she's polite, attentive and awesome!
nihon salad was good - quite expensive though. Basket of chicken was overrated. great decor though

Great venue with indoor and outdoor seating. Beautiful and feels secluded (although it's right on the heart of Orchard)
Good food and service. Check out the alfresco seating if you want to get away from Singapore's wintery air conditioning

Good food good deserts

Ribeye steak

all food is best！！！

Truffle fries and Chicken in a Basket.

Still delivering quality food after so many years.
Great ambience. Try it!
It's always nice here. The cakes especially. But brunch items like the eggs etc are nice too!
Have the leftover lasagne.  It's amazing!

Lovely place for brunch or afternoon smoothies! Get a place outdoor...

Brunch burger is quite excellent.

Friessssssss

Most of the desserts

FRENCH FRIES!!!

best place for brunch on a lazy saturday/sunday.

tasty prawn pasta👍
